last_episode_to_air.name: No Bones About It
last_episode_to_air.overview: The police arrive after Michael makes a startling discovery while digging the footings in The City Barn; Over at The Toxic Townhouse, Mike shows the homeowners the structural issues by the stairs and the dangerous gas line installation.

name: Holmes 911
overview: Mike Holmes and his children, Mike Jr. and Sherry, go back to their roots to rescue homeowners from unscrupulous contractors, unhealthy homes, and DIY projects gone wrong; the Holmes family takes on five houses, and turns them into homes again.
